The Super-Scary Theory of the 21st Century (repost)The haunting specter of techno-authoritarianism has only gotten more haunting https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-super-scary-theory-of-the-21st-a3a https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-super-scary-theory-of-the-21st-a3aNoah Smith Mon, 13 Nov 2023 15:29:33 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7014c555-d5be-4308-bef7-bb31cef8b001_1222x815.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7014c555-d5be-4308-bef7-bb31cef8b001_1222x815.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7014c555-d5be-4308-bef7-bb31cef8b001_1222x815.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7014c555-d5be-4308-bef7-bb31cef8b001_1222x815.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7014c555-d5be-4308-bef7-bb31cef8b001_1222x815.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7014c555-d5be-4308-bef7-bb31cef8b001_1222x815.jpeg" width="1222" height="815" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7014c555-d5be-4308-bef7-bb31cef8b001_1222x