。樟宜机场名列世界最佳机场<a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=best+airport+in+the+world&amp;rlz=1C1RXQR_enUS1011US1011&amp;oq=best+airport&amp;gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUqCQgBEAAYQxiKBTIGCAAQRRg5MgkIARAAGEMYigUyBwgCEAAYgAQyBwgDEAAYgAQyBwgEEAAYgAQyBwgFEAAYgAQyBwgGEAAYgAQyBwgHEAAYgAQyBwgIEAAYgAQyBwgJEAAYgATSAQgyMzI4ajBqN6gCALACAA&amp;sourceid=chrome&amp;ie=UTF-8">榜首</a>，这是有充分理由的——它有点像豪华私人休息室和巴比伦空中花园的结合体。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8d17980f-f284-44a6-a203-9b30073a5602_1192x795.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8d17980f-f284-44a6-a203-9b30073a5602_1192x795.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8d17980f-f284-44a6-a203-9b30073a5602_1192x795.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8d17980f-f284-44a6-a203-9b30073a5602_1192x795.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8d17980f-f284-44a6-a203-9b30073a5602_1192x795.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8d17980f-f284-44a6-a203-9b30073a5602_1192x795.jpeg" width="1192" height="795" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substac