div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg" width="1024" height="771" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:771,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:220030,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6aba9146-d3b2-4726-9d9a-23c8e9abfd4a_1024x771.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>美国人会将这种类型的建筑视为<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/drawing-pictures-of-cities">太阳朋克美学</a>的一部分。它提供阴凉，减少污染，让城市看起来温馨舒适。但与公园和其他绿地一样，植物覆盖的建筑也需要高昂的维护成本。在太阳能朋克的未来，这些成本可能很容易支付，因为太阳能非常便宜；在现实世界中，新加坡能够照顾好自己的绿色建筑，因为新加坡<em>真的非常富有</em>。</p><p>但也许新加坡最令人印象深刻的壮举是，尽管热带炎热潮湿，还有郁郁葱葱的绿色植物，但<em>实际上却是零虫子</em>。这是因为新加坡以近乎狂热的热情消灭了所有的虫子。这对任何城市来说都会花费很多钱，但新加坡却有很多钱可以花。</p><p>顺便说一句，新加坡是如何变得如此富有的？事实上，它的发展模式与<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-ireland-got-so-rich">爱尔兰</a>非常相似：一个非常小的英语国家，良好的教育体系，大量的高技术移民，以及不懈地注重吸引外国直接投资的产业政策。新加坡的主要投资者<a href="https://www.investmentmonitor.ai/insights/how-does-singapore-punch-above-its-weight-when-it-comes-to-attracting-fdi/">是美国</a>，对于美国企业来说，新加坡是通往亚洲的“门户”，就像爱尔兰是通往欧洲的“门户”一样。当然，这种模式不容易被大国复制，因为外国直接投资必须来自某个地方。但新加坡以惊人的技巧执行了这个小国的游戏计划——在很多方面甚至比爱尔兰更好。 （事实上​​，它在做到这一点的同时，还在一个恶劣的地理环境中生存，维护种族多样性，并保持极低的犯罪率，这更令人印象深刻，但那是另一天的故事了。）</p><p>事实上，新加坡在一个重要方面将爱尔兰远远甩在身后，那就是住房。</p><h4>住房，住房，住房！！！</h4><p>在新加坡，您立即注意到的一件事就是所有的高层住宅。它绝对无处不在。有些公寓大楼的规模看起来绝对是巨大的，与你在中国看到的类似，但看起来更漂亮： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1029830a-149b-43b9-ab53-55a0ace690c2_900x678.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1029830a-149b-43b9-ab53-55a0ace690c2_900x678.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1029830a-149b-43b9-ab53-55a0ace690c2_900x678.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1029830a-149b-43b9-ab53-55a0ace690c2_900x678.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1029830a-149b-43b9-ab53-55a0ace690c2_900x678.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1029830a-149b-43b9-ab53-55a0ace690c2_900x678.jpeg" widt